#. type: text
#: docs/zh/max_autotune_guide.md:0
msgid "# Triton-Ascend max_autotune 使用指南"
msgstr "# Triton-Ascend max_autotune Usage Guide"

#. type: text
#: docs/zh/max_autotune_guide.md:2
msgid "## 文档定位"
msgstr "## Document Positioning"

#. type: text
#: docs/zh/max_autotune_guide.md:4
msgid "本文面向已经熟悉 Triton-Ascend 自动调优机制的用户，介绍 `max_autotune` 装饰器的高级用法："
msgstr "This document is intended for users who are already familiar with the automatic tuning mechanism of Triton-Ascend, and introduces advanced usage of the `max_autotune` decorator."

#. type: text
#: docs/zh/max_autotune_guide.md:6
msgid ""
"- `max_autotune` 与标准 `@triton.autotune` 的区别与联系；\n"
"- 如何利用笛卡尔积展开机制批量生成候选配置；\n"
"- 不同 `kernel_type` 支持的调优参数及其适用场景；\n"
"- 何时选择 `max_autotune` 而非手写配置列表。\n"
msgstr ""
"- The differences and connections between `max_autotune` and the standard `@triton.autotune`;\n"
"- How to use the Cartesian product expansion mechanism to batch generate candidate configurations;\n"
"- The tuning parameters supported by different `kernel_type` and their applicable scenarios;\n"
"- When to choose `max_autotune` over manually writing configuration lists.\n"

#. type: text
#: docs/zh/max_autotune_guide.md:8
msgid "## 快速上手"
msgstr "## Quick Start"

#. type: text
#: docs/zh/max_autotune_guide.md:10
msgid "`max_autotune` 是 `@triton.autotune` 的扩展版装饰器，它允许在自动调优前将每个基础配置与额外的调优参数进行笛卡尔积展开，从而大幅减少用户需要手工枚举的配置数量。"
msgstr "`max_autotune` is an extended version of the `@triton.autotune` decorator. It allows each base configuration to be expanded via a Cartesian product with additional tuning parameters before autotuning, thereby significantly reducing the number of configurations that users need to manually enumerate."

#. type: text
#: docs/zh/max_autotune_guide.md:12
msgid "### 1. 基本用法"
msgstr "### 1. Basic Usage"

#. type: code
#: docs/zh/max_autotune_guide.md:14
msgid ""
"```python\n"
"import triton\n"
"import triton.language as tl\n"
"from triton.backends.ascend.runtime import max_autotune\n"
"\n"
"\n"
"@max_autotune(\n"
"    configs=[\n"
"        triton.Config(kwargs={'BLOCK_M': 128, 'BLOCK_N': 128}),\n"
"        triton.Config(kwargs={'BLOCK_M': 64, 'BLOCK_N': 256}),\n"
"    ],\n"
"    key=[\"M\", \"N\"],\n"
"    kernel_type=\"mix\",\n"
"    # 额外的调优参数，每个值必须是列表\n"
"    enable_hivm_auto_cv_balance=[True, False],\n"
"    tile_mix_vector_loop=[2, 4],\n"
")\n"
"@triton.jit\n"
"def kernel(\n"
"    a_ptr,\n"
"    b_ptr,\n"
"    M,\n"
"    N,\n"
"    BLOCK_M: tl.constexpr,\n"
"    BLOCK_N: tl.constexpr,\n"
"    **META\n"
"):\n"
"    ...\n"
"```\n"
msgstr ""

#. type: text
#: docs/zh/max_autotune_guide.md:16
msgid "上述配置展开后的等效配置数量为："
msgstr "The number of equivalent configurations after expanding the above configuration is:"

#. type: text
#: docs/zh/max_autotune_guide.md:18
msgid ""
"- 基础配置：2 个\n"
"- 用户提供的调优参数：`enable_hivm_auto_cv_balance`（2 种）、`tile_mix_vector_loop`（2 种）\n"
"- 使用默认值的参数：`set_workspace_multibuffer`（2 种）、`tile_mix_cube_loop`（2 种）、其他参数各 1 种\n"
msgstr ""
"- Basic configuration: 2\n"
"- User-provided tuning parameters: `enable_hivm_auto_cv_balance` (2 types), `tile_mix_vector_loop` (2 types)\n"
"- Parameters using default values: `set_workspace_multibuffer` (2 types), `tile_mix_cube_loop` (2 types), 1 type for each of the other parameters\n"

#. type: text
#: docs/zh/max_autotune_guide.md:20
msgid "总配置数量：`2 × 2 × 2 × 2 × 2 = 32` 个配置。"
msgstr "Total number of configurations: `2 × 2 × 2 × 2 × 2 = 32` configurations."

#. type: text
#: docs/zh/max_autotune_guide.md:22
msgid "> 注：`kernel_type=\"mix\"` 支持的参数较多，未显式提供的参数会使用默认值参与展开。如果希望某个参数不参与展开，可在基础 `Config` 的 `kwargs` 中固定其值。"
msgstr "Note: `kernel_type=\"mix\"` supports many parameters. Parameters not explicitly provided will use default values during expansion. If you want a specific parameter to not participate in expansion, you can fix its value in the `kwargs` of the base `Config`."

#. type: text
#: docs/zh/max_autotune_guide.md:24
msgid "### 2. `max_autotune` 与 `@triton.autotune` 的关系"
msgstr "### 2. Relationship between `max_autotune` and `@triton.autotune`"

#. type: text
#: docs/zh/max_autotune_guide.md:26
msgid "`max_autotune` 本质上是先调用 `get_max_configs` 对基础配置进行展开，然后将展开后的配置列表传递给标准的 `@triton.autotune`。因此："
msgstr "The `max_autotune` essentially first calls `get_max_configs` to expand the base configuration, and then passes the expanded configuration list to the standard `@triton.autotune`. Therefore:"

#. type: text
#: docs/zh/max_autotune_guide.md:28
msgid ""
"- 所有 `@triton.autotune` 支持的参数（`key`、`prune_configs_by`、`reset_to_zero` 等）在 `max_autotune` 中同样有效；\n"
"- `max_autotune` 额外增加了 `kernel_type` 参数和 `**tuning_params` 调优参数空间；\n"
"- 最终仍然是 `@triton.autotune` 完成 benchmark、选优和缓存。\n"
msgstr ""
"- All parameters supported by `@triton.autotune` (such as `key`, `prune_configs_by`, `reset_to_zero`, etc.) are also valid in `max_autotune`;\n"
"- `max_autotune` additionally introduces the `kernel_type` parameter and the `**tuning_params` tuning parameter space;\n"
"- Ultimately, `@triton.autotune` still handles benchmarking, optimization, and caching.\n"

#. type: text
#: docs/zh/max_autotune_guide.md:30
msgid "### 3. 必须导入 Ascend backend 扩展"
msgstr "### 3. Must import the Ascend backend extension"

#. type: text
#: docs/zh/max_autotune_guide.md:32
msgid "与使用 `configs=[]` 自动 Tiling 一样，`max_autotune` 需要 Ascend backend 扩展支持。`max_autotune` 需要从 Ascend backend 模块单独导入："
msgstr "Just like using `configs=[]` for automatic tiling, `max_autotune` requires support from the Ascend backend extension. `max_autotune` needs to be imported separately from the Ascend backend module:"

#. type: code
#: docs/zh/max_autotune_guide.md:34
msgid ""
"```python\n"
"from triton.backends.ascend.runtime import max_autotune\n"
"```\n"
msgstr ""

#. type: text
#: docs/zh/max_autotune_guide.md:36
msgid "## Kernel 类型与支持的参数"
msgstr "## Kernel Types and Supported Parameters"

#. type: text
#: docs/zh/max_autotune_guide.md:38
msgid "`max_autotune` 通过 `kernel_type` 参数区分不同类型的算子，每种类型支持不同的调优参数集合。"
msgstr "`max_autotune` distinguishes different types of operators through the `kernel_type` parameter, with each type supporting a different set of tuning parameters."

#. type: text
#: docs/zh/max_autotune_guide.md:40
msgid "### 参数支持矩阵"
msgstr "### Parameter Support Matrix"

#. type: text
#: docs/zh/max_autotune_guide.md:42
msgid ""
"| 参数 | cube | mix | vector | 默认值 | 有效值 | 说明 |\n"
"|------|:----:|:---:|:------:|--------|--------|------|\n"
"| `num_stages` | ✅ | ✅ | ✅ | `[2]` | `[1, 2]` | pipeline stages 数量 |\n"
"| `unit_flag` | ✅ | ✅ | ❌ | `[False]` | 布尔列表 | Cube 搬出相关同步优化项 |\n"
"| `limit_auto_multi_buffer_of_local_buffer` | ✅ | ✅ | ❌ | `[\"no-l0c\"]` | `[\"no-limit\", \"no-l0c\"]` | 配置 local buffer 自动 multi-buffer 的 scope |\n"
"| `limit_auto_multi_buffer_only_for_local_buffer` | ❌ | ✅ | ❌ | `[False]` | 布尔列表 | 限制自动 multi-buffer 只作用于 local buffer |\n"
"| `set_workspace_multibuffer` | ❌ | ✅ | ❌ | `[2, 4]` | `[2, 4]` | 配置 workspace multi-buffer 档位 |\n"
"| `enable_hivm_auto_cv_balance` | ❌ | ✅ | ❌ | `[True]` | 布尔列表 | 启用或禁用自动 CV balance |\n"
"| `tile_mix_vector_loop` | ❌ | ✅ | ❌ | `[2, 4]` | `[2, 4, 8]` | 配置 Vector loop 的切分份数 |\n"
"| `tile_mix_cube_loop` | ❌ | ✅ | ❌ | `[2, 4]` | `[2, 4, 8]` | 配置 Cube loop 的切分份数 |\n"
"| `enable_ubuf_saving` | ❌ | ✅ | ✅ | `[True]` | 布尔列表 | 是否启用 ubuf 节省 |\n"
msgstr ""
"| Parameter | cube | mix | vector | Default | Valid Values | Description |\n"
"|-----------|:----:|:---:|:------:|--------|--------------|-------------|\n"
"| `num_stages` | ✅ | ✅ | ✅ | `[2]` | `[1, 2]` | Number of pipeline stages |\n"
"| `unit_flag` | ✅ | ✅ | ❌ | `[False]` | Boolean list | Cube-related synchronization optimization for data movement |\n"
"| `limit_auto_multi_buffer_of_local_buffer` | ✅ | ✅ | ❌ | `[\"no-l0c\"]` | `[\"no-limit\", \"no-l0c\"]` | Configure the scope of automatic multi-buffer for local buffer |\n"
"| `limit_auto_multi_buffer_only_for_local_buffer` | ❌ | ✅ | ❌ | `[False]` | Boolean list | Restrict automatic multi-buffer to only apply to local buffer |\n"
"| `set_workspace_multibuffer` | ❌ | ✅ | ❌ | `[2, 4]` | `[2, 4]` | Configure workspace multi-buffer level |\n"
"| `enable_hivm_auto_cv_balance` | ❌ | ✅ | ❌ | `[True]` | Boolean list | Enable or disable automatic CV balance |\n"
"| `tile_mix_vector_loop` | ❌ | ✅ | ❌ | `[2, 4]` | `[2, 4, 8]` | Configure the number of splits for Vector loop |\n"
"| `tile_mix_cube_loop` | ❌ | ✅ | ❌ | `[2, 4]` | `[2, 4, 8]` | Configure the number of splits for Cube loop |\n"
"| `enable_ubuf_saving` | ❌ | ✅ | ✅ | `[True]` | Boolean list | Whether to enable ubuf saving |\n"

#. type: text
#: docs/zh/max_autotune_guide.md:44
msgid "### Kernel 类型说明"
msgstr "### Kernel Type Description"

#. type: text
#: docs/zh/max_autotune_guide.md:46
msgid ""
"- **cube**：纯 cube（矩阵乘法类）算子，支持最少的调优参数；\n"
"- **vector**：纯向量算子，仅支持 `num_stages` 和 `enable_ubuf_saving`；\n"
"- **mix**：混合 cube+vector 算子（默认类型），支持最完整的调优参数集合。\n"
msgstr ""
"- **cube**: Pure cube (matrix multiplication) operator, supporting the fewest tuning parameters;\n"
"- **vector**: Pure vector operator, only supports `num_stages` and `enable_ubuf_saving`;\n"
"- **mix**: Mixed cube+vector operator (default type), supporting the most complete set of tuning parameters.\n"

#. type: text
#: docs/zh/max_autotune_guide.md:48
msgid "## 参数值优先级与展开逻辑"
msgstr "## Parameter Value Priority and Expansion Logic"

#. type: text
#: docs/zh/max_autotune_guide.md:50
msgid "### 参数值优先级"
msgstr "### Parameter Value Priority"

#. type: text
#: docs/zh/max_autotune_guide.md:52
msgid "调优参数的值按以下优先级确定："
msgstr "The values of tuning parameters are determined according to the following priority:"

#. type: text
#: docs/zh/max_autotune_guide.md:54
msgid ""
"1. **tuning_params 参数**（最高优先级）：通过 `**tuning_params` 传递的候选值列表；\n"
"2. **基础配置中的值**：如果基础 `Config` 的 `kwargs` 中已存在该参数，则固定为该值（转换为单元素列表）；\n"
"3. **默认值**（最低优先级）：从内部默认值表获取。\n"
msgstr ""
"1. **tuning_params parameter** (highest priority): list of candidate values passed via `**tuning_params`;\n"
"2. **Value in base configuration**: if the parameter already exists in the `kwargs` of the base `Config`, it is fixed to that value (converted to a single-element list);\n"
"3. **Default value** (lowest priority): obtained from the internal default value table.\n"

#. type: text
#: docs/zh/max_autotune_guide.md:56
msgid "### 展开示例"
msgstr "### Expanded Example"

#. type: text
#: docs/zh/max_autotune_guide.md:58
msgid "假设有以下配置："
msgstr "Assume the following configuration:"

#. type: code
#: docs/zh/max_autotune_guide.md:60
msgid ""
"```python\n"
"@max_autotune(\n"
"    configs=[triton.Config(kwargs={'BLOCK_M': 128}, num_stages=2)],\n"
"    key=[\"M\", \"N\"],\n"
"    kernel_type=\"vector\",\n"
"    num_stages=[1, 2],\n"
")\n"
"@triton.jit\n"
"def kernel(...):\n"
"    ...\n"
"```\n"
msgstr ""

#. type: text
#: docs/zh/max_autotune_guide.md:62
msgid "展开过程："
msgstr "Expansion process:"

#. type: text
#: docs/zh/max_autotune_guide.md:64
msgid ""
"1. `kernel_type=\"vector\"` 支持的参数为 `num_stages` 和 `enable_ubuf_saving`；\n"
"2. `num_stages` 在 `tuning_params` 中提供 `[1, 2]`，优先级最高；\n"
"3. `enable_ubuf_saving` 未提供，使用默认值 `[True]`；\n"
"4. 笛卡尔积展开后得到 2 个配置。\n"
msgstr ""
"1. The parameters supported by `kernel_type=\"vector\"` are `num_stages` and `enable_ubuf_saving`;  \n"
"2. `num_stages` provides `[1, 2]` in `tuning_params`, with the highest priority;  \n"
"3. `enable_ubuf_saving` is not provided, so the default value `[True]` is used;  \n"
"4. After Cartesian product expansion, 2 configurations are obtained.\n"

#. type: text
#: docs/zh/max_autotune_guide.md:66
msgid "展开结果等效于："
msgstr "Expanding the result is equivalent to:"

#. type: code
#: docs/zh/max_autotune_guide.md:68
msgid ""
"```python\n"
"configs=[\n"
"    triton.Config(kwargs={'BLOCK_M': 128, 'enable_ubuf_saving': True}, num_stages=1),\n"
"    triton.Config(kwargs={'BLOCK_M': 128, 'enable_ubuf_saving': True}, num_stages=2),\n"
"]\n"
"```\n"
msgstr ""

#. type: text
#: docs/zh/max_autotune_guide.md:70
msgid "### 在基础配置中固定参数"
msgstr "### Fixing Parameters in the Base Configuration"

#. type: text
#: docs/zh/max_autotune_guide.md:72
msgid "如果希望某个调优参数不参与展开，可以在基础配置中直接固定："
msgstr "If you want a certain tuning parameter to not participate in the expansion, you can fix it directly in the base configuration:"

#. type: code
#: docs/zh/max_autotune_guide.md:74
msgid ""
"```python\n"
"@max_autotune(\n"
"    configs=[\n"
"        triton.Config(kwargs={'BLOCK_M': 128, 'enable_ubuf_saving': False}),\n"
"    ],\n"
"    key=[\"M\", \"N\"],\n"
"    kernel_type=\"vector\",\n"
"    num_stages=[1, 2],\n"
"    # enable_ubuf_saving 已在基础配置中固定为 False，不会使用默认值 [True]\n"
")\n"
"@triton.jit\n"
"def kernel(...):\n"
"    ...\n"
"```\n"
msgstr ""

#. type: text
#: docs/zh/max_autotune_guide.md:76
msgid "## 使用注意事项"
msgstr "## Usage Notes"

#. type: text
#: docs/zh/max_autotune_guide.md:78
msgid "### 1. 不支持的参数会被忽略"
msgstr "### 1. Unsupported parameters will be ignored"

#. type: text
#: docs/zh/max_autotune_guide.md:80
msgid "如果通过 `tuning_params` 传递了当前 `kernel_type` 不支持的参数，会产生警告并忽略该参数："
msgstr "If a parameter not supported by the current `kernel_type` is passed via `tuning_params`, a warning will be generated and the parameter will be ignored."

#. type: code
#: docs/zh/max_autotune_guide.md:82
msgid ""
"```python\n"
"# 警告：tile_mix_vector_loop 不支持 kernel_type=\"vector\"\n"
"@max_autotune(\n"
"    configs=[...],\n"
"    key=[\"M\"],\n"
"    kernel_type=\"vector\",\n"
"    tile_mix_vector_loop=[2, 4],  # 将被忽略并产生警告\n"
")\n"
"@triton.jit\n"
"def kernel(...):\n"
"    ...\n"
"```\n"
msgstr ""

#. type: text
#: docs/zh/max_autotune_guide.md:84
msgid "### 2. 参数值必须是列表"
msgstr "### 2. Parameter values must be lists"

#. type: text
#: docs/zh/max_autotune_guide.md:86
msgid "`tuning_params` 中的每个值必须是列表或元组，且不能为空："
msgstr "Each value in `tuning_params` must be a list or tuple and cannot be empty."

#. type: code
#: docs/zh/max_autotune_guide.md:88
msgid ""
"```python\n"
"# 正确写法\n"
"enable_hivm_auto_cv_balance=[True, False]\n"
"\n"
"# 错误写法：不是列表\n"
"enable_hivm_auto_cv_balance=True  # 将导致验证错误\n"
"```\n"
msgstr ""

#. type: text
#: docs/zh/max_autotune_guide.md:90
msgid "### 3. 配置数量增长"
msgstr "### 3. Configuration Quantity Growth"

#. type: text
#: docs/zh/max_autotune_guide.md:92
msgid ""
"展开后的配置数量等于：\n"
"基础配置数量 × Π(每个 tuning_param 的列表长度)\n"
msgstr ""
"The number of expanded configurations equals:  \n"
"Base configuration count × Π(length of each tuning_param list)\n"

#. type: text
#: docs/zh/max_autotune_guide.md:94
msgid "例如，2 个基础配置 × 3 个参数（列表长度分别为 2、3、2）= 12 个展开配置。"
msgstr "For example, 2 base configurations × 3 parameters (with list lengths of 2, 3, and 2 respectively) = 12 expanded configurations."

#. type: text
#: docs/zh/max_autotune_guide.md:96
msgid "过多的配置会增加首次调优时间，建议根据实际需要合理控制参数空间。"
msgstr "Too many configurations will increase the initial tuning time. It is recommended to reasonably control the parameter space based on actual needs."

#. type: text
#: docs/zh/max_autotune_guide.md:98
msgid "### 4. 与 `configs=[]` 的区别"
msgstr "### 4. Difference from `configs=[]`"

#. type: text
#: docs/zh/max_autotune_guide.md:100
msgid "`max_autotune` 与 `@triton.autotune(configs=[], ...)` 是两种不同的自动调优策略："
msgstr "`max_autotune` and `@triton.autotune(configs=[], ...)` are two different auto-tuning strategies:"

#. type: text
#: docs/zh/max_autotune_guide.md:102
msgid ""
"| 特性 | `max_autotune` | `@triton.autotune(configs=[])` |\n"
"|------|----------------|--------------------------------|\n"
"| Tiling 参数生成 | 需要用户在基础配置中指定 | Ascend backend 自动生成 |\n"
"| 编译参数调优 | 支持通过 `tuning_params` 展开 | 通过 `hints` 参数传入 |\n"
"| 适用场景 | 明确知道 Tiling 参数空间，需要调优编译参数 | 希望 Tiling 参数也自动生成 |\n"
msgstr ""
"| Feature | `max_autotune` | `@triton.autotune(configs=[])` |\n"
"|---------|----------------|--------------------------------|\n"
"| Tiling parameter generation | Requires user to specify in the base configuration | Automatically generated by Ascend backend |\n"
"| Compilation parameter tuning | Supported via `tuning_params` expansion | Passed through the `hints` parameter |\n"
"| Applicable scenario | When the Tiling parameter space is clearly known and compilation parameters need tuning | When Tiling parameters are also expected to be automatically generated |\n"

#. type: text
#: docs/zh/max_autotune_guide.md:104
msgid "## 进阶用法"
msgstr "## Advanced Usage"

#. type: text
#: docs/zh/max_autotune_guide.md:106
msgid "### 1. 结合多个调优参数"
msgstr "### 1. Combining Multiple Tuning Parameters"

#. type: text
#: docs/zh/max_autotune_guide.md:108
msgid "对于混合类型算子（`kernel_type=\"mix\"`），可以同时调优多个参数："
msgstr "For mixed-type operators (`kernel_type=\"mix\"`), multiple parameters can be tuned simultaneously:"

#. type: code
#: docs/zh/max_autotune_guide.md:110
msgid ""
"```python\n"
"@max_autotune(\n"
"    configs=[\n"
"        triton.Config(kwargs={'BLOCK_M': 64, 'BLOCK_N': 64}),\n"
"        triton.Config(kwargs={'BLOCK_M': 128, 'BLOCK_N': 128}),\n"
"    ],\n"
"    key=[\"M\", \"N\", \"K\"],\n"
"    kernel_type=\"mix\",\n"
"    num_stages=[1, 2],\n"
"    enable_hivm_auto_cv_balance=[True, False],\n"
"    tile_mix_vector_loop=[2, 4, 8],\n"
"    tile_mix_cube_loop=[2, 4],\n"
")\n"
"@triton.jit\n"
"def mixed_kernel(...):\n"
"    ...\n"
"```\n"
msgstr ""

#. type: text
#: docs/zh/max_autotune_guide.md:112
msgid "展开后配置数量计算："
msgstr "Expanded configuration quantity calculation:"

#. type: text
#: docs/zh/max_autotune_guide.md:114
msgid ""
"- 基础配置：2 个\n"
