#. type: text
#: docs/zh/max_autotune_guide.md:130
msgid "## 小结"
msgstr "## Summary"

#. type: text
#: docs/zh/max_autotune_guide.md:132
msgid "`max_autotune` 是 Triton-Ascend 提供的高级自动调优工具，适合以下场景："
msgstr "`max_autotune` is an advanced automatic tuning tool provided by Triton-Ascend, suitable for the following scenarios:"

#. type: text
#: docs/zh/max_autotune_guide.md:134
msgid ""
"1. 已知 Tiling 参数空间，希望减少手工枚举配置的工作量；\n"
"2. 需要联合调优多个 Ascend 编译参数（如 `num_stages`、`enable_hivm_auto_cv_balance` 等）；\n"
"3. 希望通过笛卡尔积方式批量生成候选配置。\n"
msgstr ""
"1. Given the tiling parameter space, the goal is to reduce the manual effort of enumerating configurations.  \n"
"2. Joint tuning of multiple Ascend compilation parameters (such as `num_stages`, `enable_hivm_auto_cv_balance`, etc.) is required.  \n"
"3. The aim is to batch-generate candidate configurations via Cartesian product.\n"

#. type: text
#: docs/zh/max_autotune_guide.md:136
msgid "`max_autotune` 的核心价值在于：用少量基础配置 + 调优参数空间描述，自动展开出完整的候选配置集合，兼顾了灵活性与便利性。"
msgstr "The core value of `max_autotune` lies in: using a small amount of base configuration plus a description of the tuning parameter space to automatically expand into a complete set of candidate configurations, balancing flexibility and convenience."

